Description_lang: Heavy Ordnance Inflicts $s1 Arcane damage to all nearby enemies on impact and knocks them back.Walking over this ordnance detonates it, inflicting $273720s1 Arcane damage to the target and knocking them back.Leading the boss into these bombs inflicts $273721s1 Arcane damage, stunning him and increasing his damage taken by $273721s3% for $273721d.If the ordnance is not detonated before its time expires, it explodes and inflicts $273718s1 Arcane damage to the party.
